State ex rel. GateHouse Media Ohio Holdings II, Inc.
v.
Pike Cty. Coroner's Office. 2016-1153 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 25, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied. O'Donnell and Kennedy, JJ., dissent. Frank D. Celebrezze Jr., J., of the Eighth District Court of Appeals, sitting for French, J. Robin N. Piper, J., of the Twelfth District Court of Appeals, sitting for DeWine, J.
